      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRUST A PROCESS (2) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 19.85 beating DALAIR MILO. Great chance to get the job done again. JUST TAKE IT (4) could not have been more impressive last start in his an exceptional 19.52 win at this track over 340m. Should be in this for a long way. AVA'S CARLILAH (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind JUST TAKE IT (19.92) in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Hard to beat again. HOOLIGAN MOLLY (6) is another with top-three prospects.",
